data.description: BRAND NEW ROOF & BRAND NEW AC! Beautifully renovated concrete block pool home with 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, plus den, and is situated on almost a 1/2 acre in Colonial Terrace. This home has been renovated from top to bottom. Featuring a stunning kitchen with quartz countertops, SS appliances, large kitchen island, gas stove, double ovens, oversized laundry/mud room, and luxury vinyl throughout. The pool has a built-in spa and is fully screened in and overlooks the large backyard. Plumbing has been fully re-piped. Move-in Ready!
